<item>
            <title>[LU-8094] floods of log messages seen in syslog</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8094</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;on a build of current master on el6.7 seeing a flood of reports in /var/log/messages like the following during sanity tests:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;May  3 16:47:20 centos67-2 kernel: format at mdt_handler.c:1536:mdt_getattr_name_lock doesn&apos;t end in newline&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Almost certain this is due to some recent change in master, as such messages haven&apos;t been seen before.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
